summary: This document is a subpoena issued by the Circuit Court of the Fifteenth Judicial Circuit in Palm Beach County, Florida, commanding the appearance of a witness before the State Attorney regarding an ongoing investigation. It includes instructions for compliance and emphasizes the confidentiality of the request to avoid obstructing the investigation.

persons.name: Sharon Curie
persons.context: Sharon Curie is identified as the Assistant State Attorney responsible for issuing the subpoena and overseeing the compliance process.

persons.name: Sharon Lyn Bohus
persons.context: Sharon Lyn Bohus is mentioned as a Notary Public who swore to and subscribed the document.

events.title: Issuance of Subpoena
events.description: A subpoena was issued by the Circuit Court of the Fifteenth Judicial Circuit commanding a witness to appear for interrogation in an ongoing investigation.

keyFacts: The document is a subpoena issued by the Circuit Court of the Fifteenth Judicial Circuit in Palm Beach County, Florida.
The subpoena commands a witness to appear for interrogation regarding an ongoing investigation.
The document emphasizes the confidentiality of the request to prevent obstruction of the investigation.
Sharon Curie is the Assistant State Attorney associated with this subpoena.
The subpoena was received and executed on January 17, 2006.
